UPDATE `npc_text` SET `text0_0`='The Paragons of Power are remnants from the ancient Gurubashi Empire.  We Zandalar seek them - not only are they of tremendous collectible value to us, but we believe that they also hold latent signatures of magic used by the old Empire.$B$BYou\'ll more than likely discover three kinds of Paragons in Zul\'Gurub: coins, bijous, and primal items.  Bring them to us in the quantities that we seek, and you\'ll be rewarded with some of the finest items we Zandalar have ever crafted.$B' WHERE `ID`=7634;
